Hough Transform for line detection


Author: Philip Tutzer
Date : 23.08.15
location: Vienna

Libs used: opencv 3.0 (for I/O)

This program executes the canny edge detector and applies the Hough Transform for line detection

NOTE:

- no bugfixes 
- threshold parameters as well as the camera index may be adapted
- press "d" to execute the transform, "q" to quit the program 

